                                <div id="fizzBuzz" class="tab-pane fade">
                                    <h3>FizzBuzz</h3>
                                    <div class="row h4 text-center">
                                        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                                            Enter two numbers between 1 and 100
                                            This demonstrates the Modulus Operator (division remainder)<br />
                                            If number 1 has a remainder of 0 then it gets assigned fizz<br />
                                            If number 2 has a remainder of 0 then it gets assigned buzz<br />
                                            If both numbers have a remainder of 0 then they get assigned fizzbuzz
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <form action="" name="fizzBuzzForm" id="fizzBuzzForm">
                                        <div class="form-group row rowHeight">
                                            <label for="fizzBuzzForm" class="col-md-3 col-form-label">Enter Fizz Number:</label>
